snippet.title: Ultros | Nintendo Switch & Xbox Trailer - OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Step into the surreal world of ULTROS now available on Nintendo Switch and Xbox Series X|S!

We are excited to welcome new players to our psychedelic metroidvania universe. See it come to life in a cosmic blend of space gardening, elegant close combat, and secrets to unfold.

Fans looking to delve deeper into the world of ULTROS can now pre-order Ultros: Design Works created in collaboration with Lost in Cult. This high-end art book features never-before-seen artwork, concept sketches, exclusive developer interviews and much more!

Pre-order Ultros: Design Works now: https://www.lostincult.co.uk/ 

ULTROS is out now on Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4 and PC.
http://ultrosgame.com/
